{"type":"answer","id":287059,"parentType":"question","parentId":27029,"uid":49900,"contents":"嗯...我是真的不知道偵不偵測的到啦...但就算偵測不到，那就偵測不到啊。難道阿共偵測的到F-22嗎？<br>\n<br>\n話說上面有在講印度偵測的到的，大部分的隱形戰機出門的時候都會掛信號放大器或油箱，所以偵測的到很正常，畢竟不想讓敵人知道真實的數據。<br>\n<br>\n下面是美國空軍假想敵中隊對各國匿蹤戰機的設定諸元，不一定對，但好歹有個對照。<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/EZg8tpUU0AYpuSc?format=jpg&amp;name=orig\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/EZg8tpUU0AYpuSc?format=jpg&amp;name=orig\" alt=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/EZg8tpUU0AYpuSc?format=jpg&amp;name=orig\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a>","date":"2020-06-09","agreeCount":1,"discussionCount":2}